        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
      <hr/>
    </div>

  </section>

  <section class="go">
  <div class="inner">
    <h2>Interested in Building Apps Using Lelylan?</h2>
    <a href="http://people.lelylan.com/subscriptions/new" class="button-add">Join the Beta</a>
  </div>
  </section>

</main>
